<i>noun</i>: 화친 [화친], 친화 [친화], 친선 [친선], 친분 [친분], 친목 [친목], 친교 [친교], 정의 [정의/정이], 우호 [우ː호], 우정 [우ː정], 우의 [우ː의/우ː이], 우애 [우ː애], 상종 [상종], 교유 [교유], 교분 [교분] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>화친 [화친]</dt><br>
<dd>amity; friendship; peace</dd><br>
<dd>나라와 나라 사이에 싸움이 없이 서로 가까이 지냄.</dd><br>
<dd>A state in which two or more countries are on good terms, without any fighting.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>친화 [친화]</dt><br>
<dd>harmony; friendship; affinity</dd><br>
<dd>서로 친하게 잘 어울림.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of being on friendly terms and in harmony with one another.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>친선 [친선]</dt><br>
<dd>friendship; amity</dd><br>
<dd>서로 친하고 가까워 사이가 좋음.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of two or more persons being on good terms, as they are friendly and close.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>친분 [친분]</dt><br>
<dd>closeness; friendship</dd><br>
<dd>아주 가깝고 두터운 정.</dd><br>
<dd>A very close and strong bond with someone.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>친목 [친목]</dt><br>
<dd>amity; friendship</dd><br>
<dd>서로 친하여 화목함.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of getting along and being harmonious.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>친교 [친교]</dt><br>
<dd>friendship</dd><br>
<dd>친하고 가깝게 사귐. 또는 그렇게 사귄 정.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of being close to someone; or the attachment forming in such a manner.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>정의 [정의/정이]</dt><br>
<dd>friendship; bond</dd><br>
<dd>서로 사귀어 친해진 정.</dd><br>
<dd>An emotional bond formed in a relationship.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>우호 [우ː호]</dt><br>
<dd>amity; friendship</dd><br>
<dd>개인이나 나라가 서로 사이가 좋음.</dd><br>
<dd>A state in which individuals or countries are on good terms with each other.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>우정 [우ː정]</dt><br>
<dd>friendship</dd><br>
<dd>친구 사이의 정.</dd><br>
<dd>The affection among friends.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>우의 [우ː의/우ː이]</dt><br>
<dd>friendship; fraternity; fellowship</dd><br>
<dd>친구나 형제 또는 두 집단 사이의 친밀한 감정과 의리.</dd><br>
<dd>Intimacy and fidelity between friends, siblings, or two groups.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>우애 [우ː애]</dt><br>
<dd>friendship; fraternal affection; fellowship</dd><br>
<dd>형제 또는 친구 사이의 정과 사랑.</dd><br>
<dd>Affection and love between brothers or friends.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>상종 [상종]</dt><br>
<dd>friendship</dd><br>
<dd>서로 따르며 친하게 지냄.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of accompanying each other and keeping close.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>교유 [교유]</dt><br>
<dd>friendship</dd><br>
<dd>함께 놀거나 왕래하며 사귐.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of making friends by hanging around together or keeping each other's company.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>교분 [교분]</dt><br>
<dd>intimacy; friendship</dd><br>
<dd>서로 가깝게 지내며 나눈 정.</dd><br>
<dd>Intimacy shared by keeping a close relationship.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>